snippet.title: Planet Coaster Spooky Pack OUT NOW
snippet.description:
Spooky Pack is available now to purchase for PC. A theme so dark it rose from the grave! Embrace the spook-tacular new supernatural content in Planet Coaster, and thrill your guests with surprises lurking around every dark corner! New rides, spooky scenery pieces and more! Transform your park into a gothic masterpiece.

For more news and information about Planet Coaster:

Website: https://planetcoaster.com/
Forums: https://forums.planetcoaster.com/
Facebook: https://facebook.com/PlanetCoaster
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlanetCoaster
